Name: Songs that make you feel old as shit
Description: Think songs with lyrics that make you yearn for youth, or songs celebrating milestone anniversaries that deeply unsettle you.

Name: song by a band with simultaneously the best and worst band name
I am free
Description:
Pick a song that you love but have been afraid to submit because you were worried it wouldn't be a voter-getter. 

Voting rules:
Vote for bravery. Vote for a song that might not be the catchy jam that normally stands out in Music League but that you're learning to appreciate. And think like Sam. Was this submission Jeopardy or No Jeopardy? No risk taken? Maybe no jeopardy and no vote!

Name: A song that gives you anxiety but you like it anyway
Mind Games Take 2
Description:
You know the drill: use the power of creativity to win yourself votes with your comment. Make up any comment you want.

But this time song pairing matters. Pick a song that supports your comment.

Name: Feral feminine violence
Description: "Generally you should be in the mood to join a pride of lionesses to rip a prey animal apart while listening to the song. Righteous anger, sickening grief, or a taste for revenge are all good themes but mostly - does the fem performing sound like they want to kill you? They should!"
